{{Top|leg}}
The '''Hapan Home Fleet''' was a [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] that was part of the [[Hapan Royal Navy|naval forces]] of the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]] that guarded the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]].

During the [[Second Galactic Civil War]], [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] implored [[Queen Mother]] [[Tenel Ka Djo|Tenel Ka]] to allow him to use the Home Fleet against the Confederation, which she allowed on the condition that Jacen make peace with his uncle, [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]. When [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] persuaded her that Jacen needed to be stopped, however, the Home Fleet was deployed against Jacen at the [[Battle of Kashyyyk (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Kashyyyk]].

